{"word":"G680 - ἅπτομαι - háptomai - hap'-tom-ahee - Touch","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἅπτομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">háptomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hap'-tom-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Touch</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கொளுத்து, நெருப்பை மூட்டு"},{"paragraph":"to fasten to, make adhere to; to fasten fire to a thing, to kindle, set on fire"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Reflexive of <a href=\"#/G681 - ἅπτω - háptō - hap'-to/681\">G681</a>; properly to <i>attach</i> oneself to, that is, to <i>touch</i> (in many implied relations): - touch.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}